data.description: Located just a couple blocks from beautiful downtown Northfield, this wonderful two story home has 3 bedrooms on one level, 2 full bathrooms, a nice front porch, newer stainless steel appliances, wood & tile floors,  a large deck overlooking the spacious back yard, Anderson windows, 6 panel Oak doors, Oak cabinetry, patio, back yard fire pit, storage shed, and a welcoming 3 season front porch. This quality built home is in a great location, has a detached 1 car garage, and is ready for you!!
